{"tid":552783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平涉賄】還押期間與上海能源公司通電郵　獄中教書時薪1美元","createTime":"2018-02-07T00:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T05:56:16.000Z","uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6188299c367a3b999c5b6ed76b9595dc8b8604","tid":552783,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"民政事務局前局長何志平涉嫌賄賂非洲國家政要，在美國被起訴。他在當地時間2月5日中午（本港時間2月6日凌晨）再次出庭，辯方律師庭上透露，何志平在獄中舉行講座，講述在中國創業之商機，亦開始教授課程，又大爆何志平在還押期間，仍跟上海能源公司透過電郵通訊。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n根據美國聯邦監獄管理局資料，在囚人士可使用「TRULINCS」網上系統，與親友經電郵通訊。他們需將親友資料加入聯絡人名單，獲監獄職員批准，並得聯絡人同意後，才可開始收發電郵。電郵只可包含文字，不能有附件，每封電郵最多寫1.3萬個英文字符（characters），即大約兩頁A4紙，獄方亦會檢查電郵內容。<br />\n<br />\n在獄中教書方面，美國聯邦監獄有機制讓在囚人士利用各自專長，在獄中向其他在囚人士教授課程（Inmate Instructor Program）。在此計劃下，導師會分成三個等級，第一級是本身已通過美國高中程度「普通教育發展證書考試」在囚人士，讓他們協助其他在囚人士準備考試；第二級是有專業技能人士，可以教授木工、烹飪等；第三級是「專業級別」，讓有大學以上學歷、甚至有專業資格的在囚人士教授課程。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦監獄特別為第三級導師推出獎勵計劃，犯人每小時可獲1美元報酬，更有機會獲得減刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180206/s00001/1517919166200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180206%2Fs00001%2F1517919166200&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b6ee3f40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180206%2Fs00001%2F1517919166200&h=e96e088f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180206/s00001/1517919166200</a>"},{"pid":"56eae59312b68ec60d1135d3f318c374f1f15ab3","tid":552783,"uid":52215,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"何志平可以獄中繼續推廣一帶一路"},{"pid":"49bfeef5e1cea5bff01d2443a7021f0738ec3328","tid":552783,"uid":37735,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"56eae59312b68ec60d1135d3f318c374f1f15ab3","tid":552783,"uid":52215,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"何志平可以獄中繼續推廣一帶一路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"咁咪岩<br />\n<br />\n一帶一路本身就岩堆雞鳴狗盜之人會搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cd48164824ed3ac4d78f2f082c796889225b3f","tid":552783,"uid":101328,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"56eae59312b68ec60d1135d3f318c374f1f15ab3","tid":552783,"uid":52215,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"何志平可以獄中繼續推廣一帶一路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"原來係特登入去推行一路一帶。。"},{"pid":"aae1e3c4515e6da8ee64b7654deb80bb89a85c2f","tid":552783,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"電郵可否寫中文？英文錯grammar點算？"},{"pid":"d86eb236f938f27b0f447bb49745cdb872b33b42","tid":552783,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0499c216d42d1575ad991155523e2e6d6aebb2","tid":552783,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"咁多世藝，咪入去生活囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eee4d92ae145ac72251bf4b7afb3faf9910fe8","tid":552783,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a261c9d1bd973b7d54f4e859d75dc174b4810df3","tid":552783,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"佢本身就係反面教材啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbaeba1bcfa703f031925b36691f27bf681dd12","tid":552783,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"d email會唔會寫一d 表面普通既對話<br />\n其實當中有特別暗號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9989d972e33f7f5c6b9783906166548ac3b